00:25:16.060 --> 00:25:21.440
First of all people are talking
about the web versus packaged

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:24.790
apps and how packaged
apps have these properties

00:25:24.790 --> 00:25:27.720
from security permission
prompts and so on.

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:32.570
And actually we don't
have to tie packaged apps

00:25:32.570 --> 00:25:33.990
to these prompts.

00:25:33.990 --> 00:25:40.340
In Firefox OS we use exactly the
same security model as the web.

00:25:40.340 --> 00:25:42.740
First of all, to try to have
as few prompts as possible.

00:25:42.740 --> 00:25:44.560
Like design API so
that you can do stuff

00:25:44.560 --> 00:25:47.910
