like geolocation,

00:25:50.340 --> 00:25:54.030
where we do want to prompt the
user-- even for packaged apps--

00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:55.860
we just follow the
normal web model

00:25:55.860 --> 00:25:59.370
and we ask for
permission in context.

00:25:59.370 --> 00:26:02.320
And so if there's a
TweetDeck app that

00:26:02.320 --> 00:26:05.580
needs to do some
special stuff then

00:26:05.580 --> 00:26:09.200
it can ask that at the time
when it needs to do it.

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:12.680
