is that there's

00:26:12.680 --> 00:26:13.730
two things are important.

00:26:13.730 --> 00:26:16.430
It's very important
for applications.

00:26:16.430 --> 00:26:18.910
The context of asking at
the time when you do it

00:26:18.910 --> 00:26:21.640
helps users to understand
why this happens.

00:26:21.640 --> 00:26:26.180
